    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "侍卫",
        "蔺相如"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四侍卫、蔺相如同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "威烈王坐洛阳朝政不善，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "韩、赵、魏和晋国鼎立而三。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "无公法无公理但有强权。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "抗秦楚抗韩魏又抗齐燕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "才保定吾国的大好江山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔺相如坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本公蔺相如，赵王驾前为臣。只因秦王羡我国和氏玉璧，情愿以城池十五座相"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "换。本公捧璧入秦，仍然完璧归赵。后又约赵王相会渑池。本公护驾赴会，秦"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王命赵王鼓琴，本公就请秦王击缶。秦虽然强大，总无占得便宜。赵王大悦，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "封我上卿之职，位在廉颇之上。廉颇智谋虽多，度量却小。他心中一定不服。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，话虽如此，本公总以君子待人，决不敢看人不起，先自疑惑起来，安见人"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "之度量不如我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍卫。安排车驾上朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侍卫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀大人，廉颇将军发出话来，要在大街凌辱大人。看他因大人的位分在他之上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "侍卫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心里有些不平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！廉将军堂堂一位大臣，岂有这样心事。或者他们手下人，说长道短，讲些"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是非，一旦酿出大祸，只有国家受害。你莫多言，这话我万也不信。命驾上朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自古道手下人见识浅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说是非说短长竟惹祸端。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我只当是春风吹过耳边。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "蔺相如→侍卫",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "侍卫→蔺相如",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "唱": 1,
          "白": 3
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.25,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮摇板",
          "西皮正板"
        ]
      },
      "scene_feature": [
