    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "侍卫",
        "廉颇",
        "校尉",
        "蔺相如"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急急风〗。四校尉、廉颇同上，廉颇右坐。四侍卫、蔺相如同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人说是人说非人说长短，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我把那坏话儿不挂心间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侍卫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "廉大人怒气满面挡住去路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "廉将军不过一时之怒，本公岂能与他一般见识。总是退让为是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍卫绕道而行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "廉将军也不过一时之见，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "终不能昧公理敢讲强权。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人自上场门同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "校尉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀大人，蔺大人避道而行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼，这娃娃，倒也眼亮。难道罢了不成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，绕道拦截与他。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四校尉同绕场，廉颇坐左。四侍卫、蔺相如同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一朝愤忘其身必遗国患，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他逆来我顺受方算奇男。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侍卫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "廉将军又在前面挡道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，这就不对了。本公既已退让，你反进逼。难道我相如真怕你不成。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔺相如怒，冷静。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！我既退让于先，何必相争于后。断不可因私愤而误国家大事。还是回避于"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍卫速速回府。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "蔺相如→侍卫",
          "turns": 2
        },
