    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "廉颇",
        "李贤"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李贤上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老将军太任性见识又浅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怕的是因此事将相争权。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "或不致为私仇国家不安。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廉颇上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我与他活冤家偏不相见，"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "莫非他暗地里巧设机关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军今日因何下朝甚早？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫今日并未上朝。那蔺相如在长街，两次退让，也不上朝竟自回府。恐他另"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有奸计暗害老夫。请大夫前去打探，未知尊意如何。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官情愿效劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "退让是真还是假，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "冤家宜解不宜结。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "李贤→廉颇",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "廉颇→李贤",
          "turns": 3
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
