    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "廉颇",
        "李贤"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廉颇、四校尉同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蔺相如在长街两次避躲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这件事叫老夫大费揣摩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "莫非他明退让暗害与我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "莫非他弃官职私通了外国？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "因此上我迷迷糊糊、颠颠倒倒，猜也猜不着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听李贤回来怎样说。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李贤上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蔺相如他真正聪明不过，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又有德又有量智广才多。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见老将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫回来了。少礼请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫，我命你打探之事怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你休要错怪，那蔺相如真是个和平的好人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说不是害怕大人。怕的是自己的人闹事，教秦国人借此机会亡了赵国，为此"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "常避大人。他是把国家看得要紧，私仇一毫不记。请将军不要因自己之事，误"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了国家大事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！我看相如见识甚高，老夫万万不及。赵王因而封上卿之职。但老夫"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "堂堂一位大臣，将事作错，岂不被人耻笑。也罢，既然事到这步田地，还是一"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "错再错——才不失我大臣的体统。哎呀，慢慢慢慢着！廉颇你好无才。相如也"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是一位大臣，被你几次凌辱全不计较，真乃先公后私。你怎么把这私心还要作"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到底。当了一次小人不够，还难道再当二次小人不成！哦，有了。自古将相不"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和，国家必受其累。秦国若知我们将相不合，领兵前来，那时我廉颇无谋的匹"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫，一死也不足惜。殃民误国之罪，都坐在我一人的身上……问心何安……问"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心何忍！哦，我明白了。我想这服从理法，乃是我们为大臣的本分，我不免袒"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臂负荆，亲往相府认罪，我就是这个主意了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自古道非圣贤孰能无过，"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人有过无惮改便是美德。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见识浅度量小羞煞廉颇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廉颇换衣背杖。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我今日见相如情愿受责。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廉颇、李贤同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "廉颇→李贤",
          "turns": 4
