    {
      "scene_index": 8,
      "label": "第八场",
      "characters_present": [
        "廉颇",
        "李贤",
        "蔺相如"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔺相如上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看秦人似虎狼其心叵测，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急急风〗。廉颇、李贤同上。二侍卫同追上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人廉颇前来请罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廉颇跪，蔺相如忙跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军这是何故？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前日得罪于你，不是大人退让，教我误了国家大事。来来来这是荆条一枝，求"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔺相如取条投地。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军你太多心了。请起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫非大人不恕我罪么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，将军呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "劝将军你莫要赔罪认过，"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阃以外，有我廉颇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文武同心必强国。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今二位大人，互相退让，同心辅国，和衷共济，真国家之幸也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廉颇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我二人趁今日结为金兰之好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。就请大人与我主盟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李贤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情愿效劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔺相如",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后堂安排香案，祭告天地便了。请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔺相如、廉颇同下。李贤笑，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
